Name: Verify that user can charge the battery
Description: User can easily find how to switch on/off the batter for charging.
Preconditions: User has the bike with no loaded battery and the charger.
Step by step actions to follow:
1.	Connect the battery to the bike
2.	Connect the other end to the electricity
3.	Check if the lighting marker for charging is on
4.	Wait for the battery to be fully charged
5.	Remove the battery from bike
6.	Switch on the bike.
Expected outcome: The battery is fully charged.
